rows.label: tlk0001013_msg0001
rows.name:
Now, hurry up and go see
Chairman Bahn, mo!

rows.label: tlk0001013_msg0005
rows.name:
Chairman Bahn's office is through
the shopping district and up the stairs, mo.

rows.label: tlk0001013_msg0006
rows.name:
Don't stand around loitering!
You're young, so run along, mo!

rows.label: tlk0001013_msg0007
rows.name:
So-so, I suppose, mo—
My wife left me, but other than that,
nothing's really changed, mo.

rows.label: tlk0001013_msg0011
rows.name:
Rex—
Do your best to meet the expectations
of Chairman Bahn and Punin, mo.

rows.label: tlk0001013_msg0012
rows.name:
Punin-san,
thank you for recommending me.
I'll do my best!

rows.label: tlk0001013_msg0013
rows.name:
Still, a reward worth 100 months of
Punin's salary... I'm incredibly jealous, mo—

rows.label: tlk0001013_msg0014
rows.name: (If I succeed, I'll treat him to about 10 Samod—)
